casebody.data:
Star Palace Laundry, Appellant, v. Plumb, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. April 13, 1892.) Action by the Star Palace Laundry against Almond H. Plumb.

Argued before Dwight, P. J., and Macomber and Lewis, JJ.

No opinion. Order appealed from affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
